  "description": "Provides enhanced vision in caves and dark areas.",
  "body": "<h1><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/quillphen\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support me-Patreon-ff424d?logo=patreon&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Patreon\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8GydmUN3xq\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Join our Discord-5865F2?logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\"></a> &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support me-Ko--fi-571db5?logo=kofi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\"></a></h1>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/cw/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/49b1e899a9f41e7eeeb877bc53e8d5838998a95b_0.webp\" alt=\"Patreon\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n\n# **Night Vision**\n\n\nCave Vision is a lightweight Minecraft data pack that gives all players **infinite Night Vision**, making it perfect for exploring dark caves and builds without the need for torches.\n\n---\n\n## Features\n- Grants all players **Night Vision** automatically.\n- Effect is applied silently (no swirling particles).\n- Fully compatible with **Minecraft 1.20.5+**.\n- Plug-and-play — no setup required.\n\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1294716/description_e7199d76-06d1-4492-aeab-06156c309240.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1294716/description_b57d75be-5f97-45fe-8598-81a6537e7099.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>",
